It's a spacemen, Fonzie,
and he's after me.

13:58.405 --> 14:00.282
He's...

14:00.306 --> 14:01.984
A spaceman after you?

14:02.008 --> 14:03.319
What does he want with you?

14:03.343 --> 14:04.520
Because I'm average.

14:04.544 --> 14:05.788
- I told you.
- Yeah, I know.

14:05.812 --> 14:07.022
You're right.
He said I'm humdrum,

14:07.046 --> 14:08.391
-and that's why he wants me.
- Yeah.

14:08.415 --> 14:10.059
He wants to take me
in his spaceship.

14:10.083 --> 14:12.495
Oh, make sure you get
a, uh, window seat.

14:12.519 --> 14:13.662
(laughs)

14:13.686 --> 14:15.398
Fonz, I'm not joking
around here.

14:15.422 --> 14:18.267
Yeah, it must be serious, 'cause
why else would you tempt fate?

14:18.291 --> 14:20.202
That's right, it's serious.

14:20.226 --> 14:22.104
He wants to take me
away for a bleem--

14:22.128 --> 14:23.239
that's 2,000 years.

14:23.263 --> 14:25.941
Mr. Cunningham, you are
holding on to my jacket.

14:25.965 --> 14:28.544
- Well, what should I do?
- Let go of my jacket.

14:28.568 --> 14:31.080
Hey, that's much better.

14:31.104 --> 14:33.382
Now, because you're a friend
of mine, I'll check him out.

14:33.406 --> 14:35.651
- Oh, thanks.
- Yeah. A bleem, huh?

14:35.675 --> 14:37.453
