Fonz, you see,
it's that finger of his.

15:05.638 --> 15:06.949
- Hey...
- He just points it once,

15:06.973 --> 15:08.384
and Wham, bam,
good-bye Cunningham.

15:08.408 --> 15:10.386
You ain't whistling Dixie.

15:10.410 --> 15:12.922
Hey, uh, partner,
that is some finger there

15:12.946 --> 15:14.290
you're packing, huh?

15:14.314 --> 15:17.092
Now, maybe we can work this out,
just you and me, you know?

15:17.116 --> 15:18.461
What is there to work out?

15:18.485 --> 15:19.862
It is settled.
Come along, specimen.

15:19.886 --> 15:21.730
Uh, wait a minute,
let me tell you something.

15:21.754 --> 15:23.065
You ain't taking my buddy here.

15:23.089 --> 15:25.167
You got to get through me first.

15:25.191 --> 15:28.798
Oh, splendid. A Holitacker.
I love a Holitacker.

15:30.830 --> 15:32.141
What is a Holitacker?

15:32.165 --> 15:33.943
In your language, specimen,
it is a challenge.

15:33.967 --> 15:36.645
If your champion defeats me,
you do not have to go with me.

15:36.669 --> 15:37.813
All right,
let me get this straight.

15:37.837 --> 15:40.182
If I win, you don't take
the specimen here.

15:40.206 --> 15:41.450
You read me, creature.

15:41.474 --> 15:43.919
Creature? You want to rumble?

15:43.943 --> 15:46.981
Rumble?
♪ Da, da, da, da, da. ♪

15:50.850 --> 15:53.362
That is a Holitacker.
Let us make it official.

15:53.386 --> 15:54.864
(imitates a high-pitched horn)

15:54.888 --> 15:56.932
(imitates roaring crowd)

15:56.956 --> 15:59.134
Then we must introduce
the local celebrities.

15:59.158 --> 16:02.765
(speaking high-pitched
alien language)

16:04.964 --> 16:06.475
Can we get on with this, now?

16:06.499 --> 16:08.811
Anytime you're ready.

16:08.835 --> 16:12.181
I have been challenged on
200 planets. I am undefeated.

16:12.205 --> 16:14.216
So am I.

16:14.240 --> 16:15.518
Yeah, that's right.

16:15.542 --> 16:18.120
Fonzie's never lost
a Holitacker yet.

16:18.144 --> 16:20.385
Yeah, and we got
the home planet advantage.

16:23.750 --> 16:26.629
Just count to three,
then, specimen.

16:26.653 --> 16:27.730
All right.

16:27.754 --> 16:28.764
Get him, Fonz.

16:28.788 --> 16:30.633
One, two, three!

16:30.657 --> 16:34.637
Eep! No contest.
Let's go, specimen.

16:34.661 --> 16:37.606
Wait a minute.
Fonzie, he can't just...

16:37.630 --> 16:39.308
Well...

16:39.332 --> 16:40.576
Oh, Fonz, I'm sorry.

16:40.600 --> 16:42.978
I guess the finger
was just too much.

16:43.002 --> 16:45.004
Oh.

16:51.044 --> 16:53.722
So long, buddy.

16:53.746 --> 16:56.492
Let's go.

16:56.516 --> 16:57.927
Hey, wait a minute, wait.

16:57.951 --> 16:59.662
Look at his thumb.

16:59.686 --> 17:01.797
See what he's doing
with his thumb?

17:01.821 --> 17:04.199
Impossible. This has
never happened before.

17:04.223 --> 17:07.363
Yeah, well, you never ran up
against the Fonz before, bucko.

17:13.700 --> 17:15.702
Aaayyh.

17:23.476 --> 17:24.887
So, at last, a worthy opponent.

17:24.911 --> 17:26.622
(buzzes)

17:26.646 --> 17:28.257
(electric crackling)

17:28.281 --> 17:31.760
RICHIE:
Oh, what a great story.

17:31.784 --> 17:35.561
Fonzie's thumb saving us
from that deadly alien finger.

17:36.589 --> 17:39.535
- Uncle.
- Yeah.

17:39.559 --> 17:42.104
