19:54.827 --> 19:57.501
(rapid snapping, dinging)

20:03.336 --> 20:04.847
You give up now?

20:04.871 --> 20:07.249
Nothing can top this.

20:07.273 --> 20:09.151
I put my two fingers together,

20:09.175 --> 20:10.953
and the entire
building collapses.

20:10.977 --> 20:12.621
-(hums) -Hey, wait a minute,
wait a minute!

20:12.645 --> 20:14.890
What are you talking about,
the whole building collapses?

20:14.914 --> 20:17.593
It's fantastic-- screams,
Technicolor, everything.

20:17.617 --> 20:19.728
What about the people
in the building?

20:19.752 --> 20:22.364
Wrecks them pretty bad,
kills a few, too.

20:22.388 --> 20:23.899
Well, you're in here,
too, you know.

20:23.923 --> 20:25.601
That's part of the fun.

20:25.625 --> 20:27.770
Must be a pretty tough bugger.

20:27.794 --> 20:29.338
No, not a question of toughness.

20:29.362 --> 20:31.507
I am protected by a stellar
force field. Watch.

20:31.531 --> 20:33.242
-(buzzes)
-(mouthing words)

20:33.266 --> 20:35.143
Xbuzzes)
