20:56.255 --> 20:57.432
Yeah.

20:57.456 --> 20:59.334
Good.

20:59.358 --> 21:00.636
I'll go peacefully.

21:00.660 --> 21:01.904
No, not necessary.

21:01.928 --> 21:04.039
This is the best contest
I've had in 20 bleems.

21:04.063 --> 21:05.941
The only reason I won
is because your champion

21:05.965 --> 21:07.676
cared about
his earthling friends.

21:07.700 --> 21:08.744
Funny thing, this warmth.

21:08.768 --> 21:10.145
We don't have it on Ork.

21:10.169 --> 21:12.247
We tried it once
a long time ago. Didn't work.

21:12.271 --> 21:13.409
Overpopulation.

21:15.274 --> 21:16.685
Now I must leave
your planet Earth.

21:16.709 --> 21:18.587
But I tip my kripla to you, sir.

21:18.611 --> 21:20.181
(squeaks)

21:22.515 --> 21:24.726
You're telling me that, uh,

21:24.750 --> 21:27.496
you're not taking
my pal here, right?

21:27.520 --> 21:29.598
Well, I tip
my krila to you, too.

21:29.622 --> 21:32.134
(monotone squeak)

21:32.158 --> 21:33.669
Thank you.

21:33.693 --> 21:35.370
Thank you for not taking me.

21:35.394 --> 21:37.072
Oh, I'm not taking you,
I'm taking him.

21:37.096 --> 21:38.273
Hey, get out of here.

21:38.297 --> 21:39.641
-(high-pitched tone)
-(pulsing)

21:39.665 --> 21:41.410
We need a new champion on Ork.

21:41.434 --> 21:43.345
We must now enter the time warp.

21:43.369 --> 21:45.881
(deeply, slowly): We must now
enter the time warp.

21:45.905 --> 21:47.149
Hey, wait! No, wait!

21:47.173 --> 21:48.951
You're not taking Fonzie.

21:48.975 --> 21:50.886
No, I can't let you do... do it!

21:50.910 --> 21:52.487
Why are you taking him?

21:52.511 --> 21:54.022
You don't...
I mean, he's very...

21:54.046 --> 21:56.091
Fonz, don't let him
take you like that.

21:56.115 --> 21:59.561
Please, Fonzie, don't let him!
You could stop him!

21:59.585 --> 22:02.191
(deeply, slowly):
Whoa.

22:05.224 --> 22:07.336
Fonzie?

22:07.360 --> 22:09.204
Fonz!

22:09.228 --> 22:10.505
Oh.

22:10.529 --> 22:13.375
Don't take him! No, please!

22:13.399 --> 22:14.610
Please, don't take the Fonz!

22:14.634 --> 22:15.811
No, please don't take Fonzie!

22:15.835 --> 22:17.212
- Please!
- Richard?

22:17.236 --> 22:18.881
- I'll get you some baloney!
- Richard, wake up.

22:18.905 --> 22:20.382
- If you want baloney, I'll...
- Wake up, son.

22:20.406 --> 22:22.384
What? What?

22:22.408 --> 22:24.720
Oh, you'd better
go on up to bed, dear.

22:24.744 --> 22:26.855
You fell asleep
on the couch. Come on.

22:26.879 --> 22:29.358
No, wait, see, I-l...

22:29.382 --> 22:31.593
I came home right after
I saw the flying saucer.

22:31.617 --> 22:33.862
(laughs) Another crackpot.

22:33.886 --> 22:35.364
A lot of people
thought they saw it.

22:35.388 --> 22:36.498
It was a weather balloon.

22:36.522 --> 22:38.367
We heard it on the radio
on the way home.

22:38.391 --> 22:40.202
Oh, but this was so real.

22:40.226 --> 22:41.970
And then... and then
he came down here,

22:41.994 --> 22:43.672
and he wanted to take me,
but no.

22:43.696 --> 22:45.207
No, see, I escaped to Arnold's.

22:45.231 --> 22:47.109
And then... and then,
he and Fonzie were dueling.

22:47.133 --> 22:48.944
Mork and the Fonz,
and it was a... you know,

22:48.968 --> 22:51.346
the gun versus the thumb
and the finger, and... (buzzes)

22:51.370 --> 22:53.548
- It must have been some dream.
- It was.

22:53.572 --> 22:55.284
- Good night, Richie.
- Good night, Richard.

22:55.308 --> 22:57.219
Such a cute dream, dear.

22:57.243 --> 22:59.821
You have such
a good imagination.

22:59.845 --> 23:01.490
But, uh...

23:01.514 --> 23:04.324
When I was your age,
I used to dream about girls.

23:07.420 --> 23:08.797
I'll tell you one thing.

23:08.821 --> 23:10.966
I'll settle for humdrum
any day, now.

23:10.990 --> 23:12.267
- Good night, Richard.
- Night.

23:12.291 --> 23:13.602
(knocking)

23:13.626 --> 23:15.833
Oh, don't worry, I'll get it.

23:18.998 --> 23:20.108
(sighs)

23:20.132 --> 23:21.743
Uh, excuse me, um...

23:21.767 --> 23:23.545
<i>Mark'. You're Mark'.!</i>

23:23.569 --> 23:26.682
Dad, Dad, he's...
This is Mork!

23:26.706 --> 23:28.317
