Good night, Richard.

23:28.341 --> 23:29.618
Yeah, but he's gonna
take me away!

23:29.642 --> 23:31.887
Don't you care? If you...

23:31.911 --> 23:34.089
All right, fine, you don't care.

23:34.113 --> 23:35.624
I'll be gone for about a bleem.

23:35.648 --> 23:37.492
MARION:
Wear something warm.

23:37.516 --> 23:38.593
