Let's go.

23:38.617 --> 23:40.062
Oh, that's all right.
I was lost.

23:40.086 --> 23:42.831
I was looking for directions
to highway 41, but that's okay.

23:42.855 --> 23:43.865
- No, but you're...
- I'll just...

23:43.889 --> 23:45.600
I'll just close the door
real slow.

23:45.624 --> 23:47.467
No loud noises, okay?

24:02.475 --> 24:04.720
Hey, uh, what'd you get
on the Spanish quiz, Ralph?

24:04.744 --> 24:06.121
I passed.

24:06.145 --> 24:07.756
Well, I got a B-plus.

24:07.780 --> 24:10.125
You see, now that's why
I stay up all night studying.

24:10.149 --> 24:13.662
