believe what I just saw!

24:23.362 --> 24:25.374
- Another flying saucer.
-(laughs)

24:25.398 --> 24:28.777
Better. The Hooper triplets
got new sweaters.

24:28.801 --> 24:30.781
- Come on, everybody, let's go!
- All right!

